%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22California%20is%20turning%20to%20satellites%20and%20AI%20to%20combat%20the%20next%20wave%20of%20deadly%20wildfires%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20firefighter%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20a%20burning%20structure%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67854a4f8951662c9f1fdcde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22687%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Los%20Angeles%20wildfires%20topped%20%24150%20billion%20in%20damages.%3Cp%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDevastating%20wind-fuelled%20wildfires%20caused%20havoc%20in%20southern%20California%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWith%20the%20climate%20crisis%20increasing%20the%20chances%20of%20deadly%20blazes%2C%20firefighters%20are%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20even%20the%20odds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20solution%20being%20explored%20is%20an%20AI-powered%20satellite%20constellation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20is%20turning%20to%20a%20novel%20solution%20to%20battle%20massive%20wildfires%20fuelled%20by%20global%20warming%3A%20AI-powered%20satellites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeadly%20wildfires%20devastated%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20region%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20forcing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpacific-palisades-fire-mandatory-evacuations-windstorm-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%20100%2C000%20people%20to%20evacuate%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flos-angeles-wildfires-fireproof-my-home-roofs-siding-building-code-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erazing%20thousands%20of%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDriven%20by%20freak%20environmental%20conditions%2C%20including%20prolonged%20drought%20and%20strong%20winds%2C%20the%20LA%20fires%20quickly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fla-fires-sate