0systems%20are%20often%20too%20slow%20to%20give%20firefighters%20a%20clear%20picture%20of%20these%20rapidly%20unfolding%20conflagrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20extreme%20circumstances%2C%20like%20we%20see%20in%20California%20with%20wind-driven%20fires%2C%20you%20have%20very%20little%20time%20to%20make%20those%20critical%20decisions.%20The%20faster%20you%20can%20make%20them%2C%20the%20easier%20it%20is%20to%20contain%20that%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20Collins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Firesat%20would%20significantly%20improve%20the%20ability%20to%20track%20wildfires%20compared%20to%20the%20current%20system%2C%20which%20is%20mostly%20made%20up%20of%20weather%20satellites%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%20run%20by%20the%20US%20and%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Firesat%20satellite%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bdb40cc040bd1b4ca308b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222096%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMuon%20Space's%20Firesat%20prototype%20satellite%20was%20launched%20earlier%20in%20March.%3Cp%3EMuon%20Space%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECollins%20said%20these%20satellites%20are%20designed%20to%20track%20large%2C%20intense%20fires%20and%20scan%20the%20globe%20relatively%20infrequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20the%20infrared%20sensors%20on%20Firesat's%20satellites%20will%20be%20able%20to%20track%20smaller%20low-intensity%20fires%20the%20size%20of%20a%20classroom%20and%20%E2%80%94%20once%20the%2050-satellite%20network%20is%20up%20and%20running%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20able%20to%20observe%20the%20entire%20globe%20in%2015-20-minute%20intervals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20fire%20detection%2C%20that%20is%20a%20dramatic%2C%20hundred-fold%20difference%20from%20current%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Collins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e865b987-68f9-4b95-a132-7a38b4a95320%5C%22%3EFighting%20fires%20smarter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpace%20startup%20Muon%20Space%20is%20designing%20and%20building%20the%20satellites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2014%2C%20it%20successfully%20launched%20a%20pathfinder%20prototype%20satellite%20aboard%20a%20SpaceX%20rocket.%20The%20prototype%20launch%20lays%20the%20ground%20for%20the%20planned%20launch%20of%20the%20first%20three%20Firesat%20satellites%20into%20orbit%20in%20June%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuon%20Space%20president%20Gregory%20Smirin%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20interview%20before%20the%20launch%20that%20this%20initial%20first%20phase%20will%20be%20able%20to%20scan%20every%20point%20in%20the%20globe%20twice%20a%20day%2C%20and%20be%20able%20to%20identify%20fires%20as%20small%20as%20five%20by%20five%20meters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20sparse%20data%2C%20to%20be%20polite%20about%20it%2C%20as%20to%20how%20many%20fires%20there%20are%20all%20over%20the%20world%20and%20what%20the%20incident%20rate%20is.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20to%20a%20point%20where%20we%20can%20get%20a%20much%20richer%20dataset%20about%20what%20the%20actual%20behavior%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Smirin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20able%20to%20track%20hot%20spots%20and%20fires%20early%2C%20you%20can%20even%20identify%20where%20there%20are%20maybe%20fires%20that%20might%20be%20smoldering%20or%20low%20intensity%20ahead%20of%20high%20wind%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20would%20allow%20firefighters%20to%20send%20resources%20to%20these%20smaller%20blazes%20before%20they%20become%20too%20large%20to%20contain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiresat%20also%20has%20backing%20from%20Google%20Research%2C%20and%20last%20week's%20launch%20was%20praised%20by%20Sundar%20Pichai%2C%20CEO%20of%20Google's%20parent%20company%20Alphabet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECollins%20said%20Google's%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20expertise%20would%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20sifting%20through%20the%20vast%20quantities%20of%20data%20the%20constellation%20is%20expected%20to%20generate.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20with%20the%20funding%20the%20Earth%20Fire%20Alliance%20has%20received%20from%20partners%20such%20as%20Google's%20philanthropy%20arm%20and%20the%20Gordon%20and%20Betty%20Moore%20Foundation%2C%20the%20group%20was%20committed%20to%20providing%20the%20data%20from%20Firesat%20to%20public%20safety%20agencies%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECollins%20said%20the%20Alliance%20was%20already%20partnering%20with%20fire%20responders%20such%20as%20Cal%20Fire%20to%20understand%20how%20they%20might%20use%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Cal%20Fire%20confirmed%20the%20agency's%20interest%20in%20Firesat%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Firesat%20satellite%202%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bdb4844e7cbbbe3dc46b36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20satellites%20will%20be%20designed%20and%20built%20by%20the%20end-to-end%20space%20company%20Muon%20Space.%3Cp%3EMuon%20Space%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20the%20agency's%20primary%20interest%20in%20the%20satellite%20network%20was%20in%20providing%20more%20persistent%20coverage%20of%20fires%20that%20are%20actively%20growing%20or%20being%20contained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmirin%20said%20he%20believed%20Cal%20Fire%20was%20interested%20in%20integrating%20Firesat%20into%20its%20emergency%20dispatch%20service%2C%20allowing%20the%20agency%20to%20validate%20which%20fires%20were%20growing%20quickly%20rather%20than%20wasting%20resources%20by%20dispatching%20crews%20to%20check%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20definitely%20getting%20more%20extreme%20weather%20and%20more%20frequent%20fire%2C%20and%20we're%20getting%20fire%20spreading%20in%20areas%20that%20it%20didn't%20use%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Smirin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20you're%20just%20seeing%20more%20extreme%20weather%20in%20all%20sorts%20of%20ways%2C%20and%20it's%20putting%20a%20lot%20more%20pressure%20on%20firefighters%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20respond%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-satellites-ai-to-combat-deadly-wildfires-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742471689000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bdb8634e7cbbbe3dc46b73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-satellites-ai-to-combat-deadly-wildfires-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Massive%20wildfires%20devastated%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20region%20in%20January%2C%20forcing%20over%20100%2C000%20people%20to%20evacuate%20and%20razing%20thousands%20of%20homes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-satellites-ai-to-combat-deadly-wildfires-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20flew%2016%20hours%20in%20business%20class%20with%20Cathay%20Pacific.%20The%20%245%2C444%20flight%20had%20meals%20and%20drinks%20I%20never%20imagined%20having%20on%20a%20plane.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Amber%20Gibson%20smiling%20with%20glass%20of%20wine%20on%20Cathay%20Pacific%20business%20class%20flight%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cf1fef585f1dff88b1aae7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20have%20had%20positive%20experiences%20flying%20in%20the%20Cathay%20Pacific%20business%20class.%20%3Cp%3EAmber%20Gibson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERecently%2C%20I%20took%20a%2016-hour%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness