aker%20announcement%20to%20passengers%2C%20which%20Cunard%20did%20not%20dispute%20took%20place%2C%20the%20captain%20informed%20passengers%20that%20the%20ship%20would%20be%20operating%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Bheightened%20level%20of%20security%20alertness%26quot%3B%20while%20crossing%20an%20area%20known%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-was-held-hostage-by-pirates-for-8-months-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epiracy%20threats.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20these%20security%20measures%2C%20passengers%20were%20told%20over%20the%20loudspeaker%20that%20the%20external%20promenade%20decks%20would%20be%20closed%20overnight%2C%20and%20only%20essential%20open-deck%20lights%20would%20remain%20on%20to%20minimize%20the%20ship's%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPassengers%20were%20also%20asked%20to%20turn%20off%20their%20stateroom%20lights%20when%20not%20needed%20and%20to%20keep%20their%20curtains%20drawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Queen%20Anne%20is%20Cunard's%20fourth%20luxury%20cruise%20ship.%20It%20can%20accommodate%202%2C996%20guests%2C%20as%20well%20as%201%2C225%20crew%2C%20and%20has%20thousands%20of%20pieces%20of%20art%20on%20board%2C%20as%20well%20as%20facilities%20for%20activities%20like%20archery%20and%20pickleball.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20waters%20between%20Indonesia%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20the%20Philippines%20were%20once%20notorious%20for%20kidnapping-for-ransom%20incidents%2C%20particularly%20by%20the%20Abu%20Sayyaf%20Group%2C%20a%20jihadist%20militant%20and%20pirate%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20late%202016%20and%20mid-2022%2C%20ships%20were%20advised%20to%20avoid%20the%20area%2C%20with%20ReCAaP's%20Information%20Sharing%20Center%2C%20which%20tracks%20piracy%20in%20Asia%2C%20deeming%20the%20threat%20of%20abduction%20to%20be%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20abduction%20incidents%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20the%20area%20since%20January%202020%2C%20and%20the%20threat%20level%20was%20downgraded%20to%20%26quot%3Blow%2