caption%3ESteven%20took%20advantage%20of%20affordable%20flights%20to%20travel%20around%20the%20region%20on%20weekends.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Catudal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20buy-in%20from%20everyone%20on%20the%20team%20to%20ensure%20projects%20were%20successful.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20Saudis%20who%20I%20worked%20with%20said%20that%20they%20studied%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Europe%20but%20chose%20to%20come%20back%20because%20they%20wanted%20to%20help%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvision-2030-saudi-arabia-plan-future-proof-oil-economy-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20people%20I%20worked%20with%20had%20a%20ton%20of%20passion%20and%20pride%20toward%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20was%20the%20same%20intensity%20of%20every%20consulting%20project.%20There%20are%20tight%20deadlines%2C%20and%20some%20weeks%2C%20it's%20a%20grind%20to%20get%20everything%20done.%20On%20weekends%20when%20colleagues%20had%20traveled%20to%20the%20region%20for%20work%2C%20we%20got%20our%20heads%20down%20and%20it%20could%20be%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20projects%20in%20the%20region%20that%20are%20remote%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeloitte-ey-pwc-kpmg-hybrid-work-policies-return-office-rto-2025-2%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHere%2520are%2520the%2520RTO%2520policies%2CKPMG%252C%2520EY%252C%2520and%2520PwC.%26amp%3Btext%3DMany%2520big%2520companies%2520are%2520pulling%2Con%2520hybrid%2520work%2520in%25202025.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20was%20always%20in%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiyadh%20is%20a%20massive%20city%20and%20is%20very%20spread%20out.%20I%20took%20a%20cab%20to%20and%20from%20work%2C%20partly%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20air%20conditioning%20and%20avoid%20the%20heat.%20In%20the%20summer%2C%20it's%20close%20to%20110%20degrees.%20I%20found%20the%20heat%20challenging%2C%20especially%20trying%20to%20stay%20cool%20before%20client%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261c3fb63-8776-47c5-afc6-bb1d9e8c0dfa%5C%22%3EThe%20lifestyle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20very%20easy%20to%20travel%20around%20the%20region%20on%20the%20weekends.%20There%20are%20loads%20of%20affordable%20flights%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20find%20a%20%24100%20return%20deal.%20I%20went%20to%20Oman%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Morocco%2C%20Cairo%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20Qatar%2C%20and%20Georgia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiyadh%20itself%20is%20bustling%20and%20energetic.%20I%20loved%20the%20evening%20culture%20once%20it%20had%20cooled%20down%20a%20bit.%20Even%20at%2011%20p.m.%2C%20thousands%20of%20people%20and%20kids%20would%20be%20out%20walking%20or%20playing%20soccer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20always%20new%20things%20to%20do%2C%20it%20was%20very%20fun%20and%20felt%2C%20to%20me%2C%20like%20safe%20place%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tahlia%20Street%20in%20Riyadh%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ceddf9585f1dff88b19fed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETahlia%20Street%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20commercial%20hubs%20in%20Riyadh%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3Cp%3EJohannes%20Sadek%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20most%20was%20how%20friendly%20the%20Saudis%20I%20met%20were%20to%20me%20and%20how%20welcomed%20I%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20a%20country%20where%20all%20the%20signs%20were%20in%20a%20different%20language%20and%20I%20couldn't%20order%20in%20restaurants%20wasn't%20a%20problem.%20People%20were%20always%20pulling%20out%20their%20phones%2C%20trying%20to%20translate%20and%20figure%20out%20what%20I%20was%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20same%20with%20my%20colleagues%20and%20clients.%20People%20were%20always%20welcoming%20me%20into%20their%20home%2C%20asking%20to%20get%20meals%20or%20giving%20me%20recommendations.%20After%20work%2C%20I%20was%20often%20invited%20to%20join%20in%20scoccer%20games%20or%20invited%20to%20colleagues'%20houses%20for%20dinner.%20They'd%20even%20offer%20to%20drive%20me%20home%20rather%20than%20take%20a%20cab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20toughest%20things%20was%20being%20away%20from%20friends%20and%20family%20and%20keeping%20in%20contact%20around%20the%20time%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20consulting%20projects%20vary%20in%20length%2C%20from%20one%20or%20two%20months%20to%20up%20to%20a%20year.%20While%20you're%20away%2C%20it%20can%20feel%20like%20your%20life%20is%20on%20pause.%20You%20miss%20friends%20getting%20engaged%20or%20cousins%20going%20to%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2222798fdb-c11b-4a35-9606-2dec95539975%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECareer%20growth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20a%20project%20abroad%20is%20absolutely%20worth%20it.%20I'll%20take%20this%20experience%20with%20me%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20difference%20I%20noticed%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20was%20the%20direct%20approach%20that%20individuals%20took%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20was%20consensus%20among%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20in%20New%20York%2C%20once%20a%20decision%20had%20been%20made%2C%20it%20was%20assumed%20everyone%20agreed%20and%20it%20wasn't%20questioned.%20However%2C%20while%20working%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20there%20were%20many%20times%20when%20everyone's%20input%20was%20requested%20after%20a%20decision%20was%20made%20to%20ensure%20that%20everyone%20was%20onboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20in%20such%20a%20diverse%20office%20culture%20made%20me%20think%20about%20how%20peoples'%20background%20impacts%20how%20they%20work%20and%20deal%20with%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20future%2C%20if%20a%20team%20is%20working%20from%20one%20perspective%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20experience%20opens%20up%20your%20mind%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20other%20ways%20you%20can%20tackle%20and%20solve%20this%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20career%20as%20a%20consultant%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Apthompson%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Epthompson%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-abroad-saudi-arabia-middle-east-consultant-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742469661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c07bfab8b41a9673f928b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-abroad-saudi-arabia-middle-east-consultant-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Steven%20Catudal%2C%20a%20consultant%20working%20in%20New%20York%2C%20moved%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia%20for%20six%20months.%20He%20shared%20what%20working%20in%20Riyadh%20was%20like.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pthompson%40businessinsider.com%20(Polly%20Thompson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-abroad-saudi-arabia-middle-east-consultant-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata-backed%20Air%20India%20eyes%20major%20widebody%20jet%20order%20from%20Airbus%20and%20Boeing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742469631000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-air-india-widebody-jet-order-airbus-boeing-india-aviation-125032000843_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Air%20India%20may%20be%20looking%20to%20add%2030%20to%2040%20jets%20as%20Tata%20Group%20plans%20domestic%20and%20international%20expansion%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonica