20new%20ball.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BToo%20Reliant%20On%20US%26quot%3B%3F%20Why%20Canada%20PM%20Chose%20Europe%20Over%20US%20As%20First%20Foreign%20Visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada's%20new%20prime%20minister%2C%20Mark%20Carney%2C%20has%20made%20a%20bold%20move%20by%20choosing%20Europe%20as%20the%20destination%20for%20his%20first%20foreign%20visit%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20traditional%20choice%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20This%20decision%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20been%20attacking%20Canada's%20sovereignty%20and%20economy.%20Carney's%20first%20stop%20was%20Paris%2C%20where%20he%20met%20with%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%2C%20and%20then%20he%20headed%20to%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20current%20international%20context%2C%20we%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20develop%20our%20most%20strategic%20projects%20with%20our%20closest%2C%20more%20loyal%20partners%2C%E2%80%9D%20Macron%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20stronger%20together%2C%20better%20able%20to%20ensure%20the%20respect%20of%20our%20interests%2C%20the%20full%20exercise%20of%20our%20sovereignty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20visit%2C%20Carney%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20strengthening%20ties%20with%20reliable%20allies%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Trump's%20aggressive%20trade%20policies.%20He%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20France%20and%20the%20whole%20of%20Europe%20works%20enthusiastically%20with%20Canada%2C%20the%20most%20European%20of%20non-European%20countries%2C%20determined%20like%20you%20to%20maintain%20the%20most%20positive%20possible%20relations%20with%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%20Carney's%20visit%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20showcase%20Canada's%20deep%20European%20bonds%20and%20to%20display%20his%20gravitas%20on%20the%20world%20stage%20as%20he%20prepares%20for%20an%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20talks%20with%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Starmer%20in%20London%2C%20Carney%20told%20journalists%20his%20country%20%26quot%3Bmust%20diversify%26quot%3B%20its%20trade%20and%20security%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20clear%20is%20that%20our%20trade%20and%20our%20security%20relations%20are%20too%20reliant%20on%20the%20United%20States.%20We%20must%20diversify%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarney's%20decision%20to%20visit%20Europe%20first%20is%20also%20seen%20as%20a%20strategic%20move%20to%20counter%20Trump's%20attacks%20on%20Canada's%20sovereignty.%20Trump%20has%20imposed%20tariffs%20on%20Canadian%20goods%20and%20has%20threatened%20to%20impose%20even%20more%20levies%2C%20which%20has%20had%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20Canadian%20economy.%20Canada%20has%20retaliated%20with%20its%20own%20tariffs%20on%20American%20goods%2C%20but%20Carney%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20looking%20for%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20is%20to%20have%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20discussion%20of%20a%20negotiation%20of%20our%20overall%20commercial%20and%20security%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr.%20Carney%20told%20the%20media%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarney's%20visit%20to%20Europe%20was%20also%20significant%20because%20of%20his%20personal%20ties%20to%20the%20region.%20His%20wife%20is%20British%2C%20and%20he%20studied%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford.%20He%20also%20served%20as%20the%20governor%20of%20the%20Bank%20of%20England%2C%20making%20him%20the%20first%20foreigner%20to%20hold%20the%20position.%20He%20gained%20his%20British%20citizenship%20in%202018%2C%20but%20has%20moved%20to%20renounce%20his%20British%20citizenship%20and%20Irish%20citizenship%20by%20birth%20because%20of%20his%20prime%20ministerial%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20symbolism%20of%20Carney's%20European%20tour%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20Canada's%20relationship%20with%20the%20United%20States%20is%20complex%20and%20multifaceted.%20The%20United%20States%20is%20Canada's%20top%20trading%20partner%2C%20with%20about%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20Canadian%20exports%20going%20to%20the%20US.%20However%2C%20Carney%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20is%20looking%20to%20diversify%20Canada's%20trade%20relationships%20and%20to%20strengthen%20ties%20with%20other%20reliable%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Trump's%20rhetoric%20about%20annexing%20Canada%2C%20Carney%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bunthinkable%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20United%20States%20would%20make%20such%20a%20move.%20He%20also%20emphasised%20that%20both%20Canada%20and%20the%20US%20are%20members%20of%20NATO%2C%20highlighting%20the%20importance%20of%20their%20shared%20security%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Carney's%20European%20tour%20was%20a%20significant%20move%20in%20his%20efforts%20to%20strengthen%20Canada's%20relationships%20with%20its%20allies%20and%20to%20counter%20Trump's%20attacks%20on%20Canada's%20sovereignty.%20As%20he%20prepares%20for%20an%20election%2C%20Carney%20will%20need%20to%20continue%20to%20navigate%20the%20complex%20web%20of%20international%20relationships%20and%20to%20make%20tough%20decisions%20about%20Canada's%20place%20in%20the%20world.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742468820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F8a3uedv8_mark-carney-keir-starmer-reuters_625x300_20_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftoo-reliant-on-us-why-canada-pm-mark-carney-chose-europe-over-us-as-first-foreign-visit-7968288%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20his%20visit%2C%20Carney%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20strengthening%20ties%20with%20reliable%20allies%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Trump's%20aggressive%20trade%20policies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftoo-reliant-on-us-why-canada-pm-mark-carney-chose-europe-over-us-as-first-foreign-visit-7968288%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indonesia's%20Richest%20Woman%2C%20Marina%20Budiman%2C%20Loses%20%243.6%20Billion%20In%20Just%203%20Days%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMarina%20Budiman%20has%20lost%20her%20spot%20as%20Indonesia's%20richest%20woman%20after%20losing%20%243.6%20billion%20in%20just%20three%20days.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%20(SCMP)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Ms%20Budiman%2C%20the%20co-founder%20and%20president%20commissioner%20of%20data%20centre%20company%20DCI%20Indonesia%2C%20was%20making%20%24350%20million%20each%20day%2C%20which%20propelled%20her%20net%20worth%20to%20%247.5%20billion.%20However%2C%20three%20weeks%20later%2C%20she%20lost%20almost%20half%20of%20her%20net%20worth%20after%20the%20shares%20of%20her%20firm%20came%20crashing%20down.%20She%20wasn't%20the%20only%20one%20hit.%20Her%20fellow%20billionaires%20and%20co-founders%2C%20Otto%20Toto%20Sugiri%20and%20Han%20Arming%20Hanafia%2C%20also%20saw%20their%20combined%20net%20worth%20soar%20by%20over%20%2417%20billion%20before%20they%20plummeted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fasia%2Fsoutheast-asia%2Farticle%2F3302969%2Findonesias-richest-woman-marina-budiman-loses-half-her-wealth-3-days%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20DCI%20closed%20on%20Tuesday%20with%20a%20market%20value%20of%20close%20to%20%2417%20billion%2C%20compared%20to%20last%20year's%20revenue%20of%20%24112%20million%20and%20%2449%20million%20profit.%20The%20company's%20stock%20was%20trading%20at%20416%20times%20its%20earnings%2C%20making%20it%20the%20most%20expensive%20stock%20among%20comparable%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20the%20crash%20of%20DCI%20Indonesia's%20shares%2C%20Ms%20Budiman's%20wealth%20dropped%20by%20half.%20This%20could%20be%20yet%20another%20addition%20to%20the%20country's%20infamous%20boom-and-bust%20stock%20price%20run.%20One%20of%20the%20reasons%20behind%20this%20is%20low%20liquidity.%20Many%20Indonesian%20companies%20have%20stocks%20that%20aren't%20frequently%20bought%20or%20sold.%20So%2C%20when%20a%20stock%20is%20thinly%20traded%2C%20even%20small%20orders%20can%20cause%20big%20price%20movements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDCI%20shares%20took%20a%20hit%20because%2078%25%20of%20shares%20are%20owned%20by%20only%20four%20people.%20Since%20most%20shares%20are%20held%20by%20a%20small%20group%2C%20only%20a%20tiny%20fraction%20is%20available%20for%20public%20trading.%20So%2C%20of%20the%202.4%20billion%20outstanding%20DCI%20shares%2C%20just%2080%2C400%20shares%20changed%20hands%20by%20midday%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20Jakarta%20compared%20with%20millions%20at%20companies%20in%20Indonesia%20of%20a%20similar%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrench-scientist-denied-entry-to-us-after-officials-find-texts-critical-of-trump-on-his-phone-7967744%5C%22%3EFrench%20Scientist%20Denied%20Entry%20To%20US%20After%20Officials%20Find%20Texts%20Critical%20Of%20Trump%20On%20His%20Phone%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDCI's%20price%20swings%20%26quot%3Bare%20largely%20a%20function%20of%20its%20tight%20free%20float.%20Bid-offer%20spreads%20are%20narrow%2C%20so%20any%20substantial%20positioning%20can%20move%20the%20stock%20significantly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mohit%20Mirpuri%2C%20a%20fund%20manager%20at%20SGMC%20Capital%20Pte%20in%20Singapore%2C%20as%20per%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20wild%20price%20swings%20in%20stocks%20are%20a%20common%20and%20increasingly%20problematic%20feature%20of%20Indonesia's%20equity%20market.%20Dozens%20of%20firms%20have%20moved%20by%201%2C000%25%20or%20more%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20their%20shares%20seemingly%20unshackled%20from%20the%20underlying%20financials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20DCI's%20case%2C%20the%20rapid%20price%20hike%20in%20shares%20was%20fueled%20by%20investor%20confidence%20because%20of%20the%20rising%20demand%20for%20centres.%20Foreign%20investments%20also%20played%20a%20role.%20For%20example%2C%20Oracle%20Corp.%20is%20in%20discussions%20with%20Indonesia's%20government%20to%20establish%20a%20cloud%20services%20centre%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742468760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fg5netorg_marina-budiman_625x300_20_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmarina-budiman-indonesias-richest-woman-loses-3-6-billion-in-just-3-days-7968189%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Marina%20Budiman%20has%20lost%20her%20spot%20as%20Indonesia's%20richest%20woman%20after%20losing%20%243.6%20billion%20in%20just%20three%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmarina-budiman-indonesias-richest-woman-loses-3-6-billion-in-just-3-days-7968189%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221%25%20Conviction%20Rate%20Against%20Politicians%20Leaves%20Probe%20Agency%20ED%20Red-Faced%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20was%20busy%20questioning%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Yadav%20in%20Patna%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Centre%20informed%20Parliament%20that%20the%20conviction%20rate%20of%20the%20probe%20agency%20in%20terms%20of%20cases%20against%20politicians%20has%20been%20about%20one%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20past%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20as%20many%20as%20193%20cases%20against%20politicians%20have%20been%20registered%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20which%20only%20two%20convictions%20have%20been%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Finance%20Pankaj%20Chaudhary%20informed%20the%20%C2%A0Rajya%20Sabha.%20Of%20the%20total%20cases%2C%20138%20-%20or%2071%25%20-%20%C2%A0have%20been%20registered%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%20(since%202019)%20after%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20for%20a%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20both%20convictions%20by%20the%20ED%20are%20of%20political%20leaders%20from%20Jharkhand.%20Former%20state%20minister%20Hari%20Narayan%20Rai%20was%20sentenced%20to%20seven%20years%20of%20rigorous%20imprisonment%20and%20fined%20Rs%205%20lakh%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20in%202017%2C%20while%20another%20former%20minister%20from%20the%20state%2C%20Anosh%20Ekka%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%20seven%20years'%20rigorous%20imprisonment%20and%20slapped%20with%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%202%20crore%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20probed%20both%20leaders%20as%20part%20of%20a%20money-laundering%20investigation%20against%20former%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Madhu%20Koda.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20whether%20they%20appealed%20against%20the%20sentences%20pronounced%20by%20special%20PMLA%20courts%20in%20Ranchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20data%20of%20ED%20cases%20registered%20against%20MPs%2C%20MLAs%20%26amp%3B%20local%20administrators%20along%20with%20their%20party%2C%20state-wise%2C%20is%20not%20maintained.%20However%2C%20the%20year-wise%20details%20of%20cases%20against%20existing%20and%20former%20MPs%2C%20MLAs%2C%20MLCs%20and%20political%20leaders%20or%20anyone%20affiliated%20with%20any%20political%20party%20is%20being%20shared%2C%26quot%3B%20minister%20Chaudhary%20informed%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20Ammo%20For%20Opposition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20ministry%20revealed%20that%20of%20the%20193%20cases%20registered%20against%20politicians%2C%20138%20were%20filed%20since%202019%20and%2032%20between%20April%202022%20and%20March%202023%20alone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20often%20accused%20the%20Centre%20of%20using%20agencies%20like%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20for%20political%20ends%20and%20this%20disclosure%20has%20given%20them%20more%20ammunition.%20The%20Congress%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20for%20using%20central%20investigating%20agencies%20to%20intimidate%20political%20opponents%20and%20alleged%20that%20ED%20summons%20are%20sent%20to%20leaders%20from%20opposition%20parties%20every%20time%20an%20election%20approaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20spokesperson%20Supriya%20Shrinate%20also%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20converting%20the%20ED%20into%20a%20'front'%20of%20the%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20elections%20approach%20-%20PM%20Narendra%20Modii%2C%20who%20sent%20ED%20summons%20to%20the%20opposition%2C%20has%20made%20ED%20a%20front%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Shrinate%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finance%20Ministry%2C%20however%2C%20told%20the%20Parliament%20that%20ED%20takes%20up%20cases%20for%20investigation%20based%20on%20credible%20evidence%2Fmaterial%20and%20not%20on%20political%20affiliations%2C%20religion%20or%20otherwise.%20The%20actions%20of%20the%20ED%2C%20%C2%A0the%20Centre%20pointed%20out%2C%20are%20always%20open%20to%20judicial%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agency%20is%20accountable%20to%20different%20judicial%20forums%20viz.%20adjudicating%20authority%2C%20appellate%20tribunal%2C%20special%20courts%2C%20honourable%20High%20Court%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20the%20actions%20taken%20in%20the%20course%20of%20implementation%20of%20the%20PMLA%2C%202002%3B%20FEMA%20(Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act)%2C%201999%20and%20FEOA%20(Fugitive%20Economic%20Offenders%20Act)%2C%202018%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20the%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20low%20rate%20of%20convictions%20in%20high-profile%20cases%20has%20also%20left%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20red-faced.%20NDTV%20has%20learnt%20that%20after%20several%20Supreme%20Court%20observations%2C%20the%20agency%20decided%20not%20to%20rely%20solely%20on%20%26quot%3Bcriminal%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bpredicate%20offence%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20which%20it%20registers%20such%20cases.%20It%20will%20now%20also%20include%20the%20offence%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20related%20to%20the%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstructions%20to%20this%20effect%20were%20cleared%20by%20ED%20Director%20Rahul%20Navin%20last%20year%20and%20have%20been%20passed%20on%20to%20officers%20who%20are%20probing%20high-profile%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742468580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fe8pp16_ed-generic_625x300_16_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-finance-ministry-centre-parliament-1-conviction-rate-against-politicians-leaves-probe-agency-ed-red-faced-7968266%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20a%20time%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20was%20busy%20questioning%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Yadav%20in%20Patna%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Centre%20informed%20Parliament%20that%20the%20conviction%20rate%20of%20the%20probe%20agency%20in%20terms%20of%20cases%20against%20politicians%20has%20been%20about%201%25%20in%2010%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-finance-ministry-centre-parliament-1-conviction-rate-against-politicians-leaves-probe-agency-ed-red-faced-7968266%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sweden%20to%20invest%20%2430%20million%20in%20school%20security%20after%20mass%20shooting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742