o%20fully%20embrace%20life%20abroad%20and%20press%20pause%20on%20an%20otherwise%20hectic%20and%20demanding%20schedule.%20When%20July%202023%20arrived%2C%20it%20was%20back%20to%20the%20script%2C%20back%20to%20normal%20life%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20my%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20plan%20was%20further%20solidified%20when%20I%20was%20accepted%20to%20medical%20school%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-visited-scotland-biggest-tourist-mistakes-cities-highlands-weather-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earriving%20in%20Edinburgh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20deferred%20until%202023%20when%20I'd%20be%20back%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20returned%20irrevocably%20changed%2C%20a%20new%20person%20with%20new%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a173894-3097-4a5a-8096-53dcfa06974d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'd%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20physician%20since%20I%20was%20a%20teenager%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20I'd%20wanted%20to%20help%20reduce%20the%20prevalence%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fobesity-economic-cost-4-trillion-wegovy-ozempic-weight-loss-drugs-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echronic%20conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20cardiovascular%20disease%20and%20obesity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20estimates%20that%20non-communicable%20diseases%20are%20responsible%20for%2075%25%20of%20deaths%20globally%20and%20that%20an%20estimated%2080%25%20are%20preventable%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirement-high-stress-career-restored-my-health-slow-travel-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elifestyle%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20the%20keys%20to%20a%20healthier%20population%20are%20reducing%20behavioral%20and%20environmental%20risk%20factors%2C%20addressing%20socioeconomic%20inequity%2C%20and%20investing%20in%20widespread%20preventive%20health%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mission%20revolved%20around%20this.%20And%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20while%20living%20in%20Edinburgh%2C%20I%20got%20a%20taste%20of%20what%20this%20looked%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20inherent%20walkable%20nature%20of%20living%20in%20a%20European%20city%2C%20combined%20with%20safe%20and%20reliable%20public%20transportation%2C%20led%20to%20us%20forgoing%20a%20car.%20Food%20was%20more%20affordable%20here%2C%20locally%20produced%2C%20and%20less%20processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommon%20additives%20found%20in%20many%20US%20products%20were%20banned%2C%20and%20food%20generally%20contained%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsome-ultra-processed-foods-may-be-healthier-than-homemade-scientist-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efewer%20preservatives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20we%20made%20daily%20trips%20to%20the%20market%20or%20grocery%20store.%20And%20Scotland's%20public%20universal%20healthcare%20system%2C%20although%20not%20perfect%2C%20offers%20high-quality%2C%20affordable%20medical%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20my%20definition%20of%20success%2C%20honed%20in%20America's%20hustle%20culture%2C%20changed.%20Prestigious%20careers%20and%20high%20salaries%20became%20secondary%20to%20my%20increased%20quality%20of%20life%20and%20availability%20of%20time.%20Through%20learning%20to%20live%20intentionally%20and%20mindfully%2C%20my%20nervous%20system%20became%20more%20regulated%2C%20and%20I%20found%20the%20peace%20I%20had%20been%20searching%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20over%2010%20years%2C%20I%20was%20chasing%20the%20dream.%20Yet%2C%20I%20began%20to%20ask%20myself%20if%20it%20was%20really%20mine%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3c05cad-9600-4256-91dc-655e93728f40%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShortly%20after%20returning%20to%20the%20US%20in%202023%2C%20I%20dropped%20out%20of%20medical%20school%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20of%20the%20reasons%20telling%20me%20to%20stay%20abroad