ms%20and%20Border%20Protection%20officials%20found%20messages%20on%20his%20devices%20that%20were%20critical%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20policies%20on%20research%20funding%20and%20scientific%20priorities%2C%20describing%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Bhateful%20and%20conspiratorial%26quot%3B%20and%20potentially%20linked%20to%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researcher's%20equipment%20was%20confiscated%2C%20and%20he%20was%20put%20on%20a%20plane%20back%20to%20Europe%20the%20following%20day.%C2%A0The%20French%20government%20has%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20incident%2C%20highlighting%20the%20growing%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20measure%20was%20apparently%20taken%20by%20the%20American%20authorities%20because%20the%20researcher's%20phone%20contained%20exchanges%20with%20colleagues%20and%20friends%20in%20which%20he%20expressed%20a%20personal%20opinion%20on%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20research%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Philippe%20Baptiste%2C%20France's%20minister%20of%20higher%20education%20and%20research%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20AFP%2C%20published%20by%20French%20newspaper%20Le%20Monde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFreedom%20of%20opinion%2C%20free%20research%2C%20and%20academic%20freedom%20are%20values%20%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8Bthat%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20proudly%20uphold.%20I%20will%20defend%20the%20right%20of%20all%20French%20researchers%20to%20be%20faithful%20to%20them%2C%20while%20respecting%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20French%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20has%20acknowledged%20the%20US's%20sovereign%20right%20to%20decide%20who%20enters%20its%20country%2C%20while%20also%20expressing%20disappointment%20over%20the%20situation.%20The%20ministry%20emphasised%20France's%20commitment%20to%20academic%20and%20scientific%20cooperation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20desire%20to%20promote%20freedom%20of%20expression.%C2%A0%