Url%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chahal-Dhanashree%20Divorce%20Granted%20By%20Court%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%20Longer%20Husband%20And%20Wife%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20team%20spinner%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yuzvendra%20Chahal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1394-yuzvendra-chahal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYuzvendra%20Chahal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Dhanashree%20Verma%20on%20Thursday%20were%20granted%20the%20decree%20of%20divorce%20by%20the%20Mumbai%20family%20court.%20Chahal's%20lawyer%2C%20Nitin%20Kumar%20Gupta%2C%20confirmed%20the%20development%20while%20speaking%20to%20reporters%20outside%20the%20court.%20%26quot%3BThe%20court%20has%20granted%20the%20decree%20of%20divorce.%20The%20court%20has%20accepted%20the%20joint%20petition%20of%20both%20parties.%20The%20parties%20are%20no%20longer%20husband%20and%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20advocate%20Nitin%20said%20in%20a%20video%20by%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1902648899145470011%5C%22%3E%20ANI%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChahal%20and%20Verma%20got%20married%20in%20December%202020.%20As%20per%20their%20petition%2C%20they%20separated%20in%20June%202022.%20On%20February%205%2C%20they%20filed%20a%20joint%20petition%20before%20the%20family%20court%20seeking%20divorce%20by%20mutual%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20requested%20the%20family%20court%20to%20decide%20the%20divorce%20plea%20by%20Thursday%2C%20considering%20the%20fact%20that%20Chahal%20would%20not%20be%20available%20later%20as%20he%20is%20participating%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20cricket%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IPL%20T20%20cricket%20tournament%20is%20scheduled%20to%20start%20from%20March%2022.%20Chahal%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Punjab%20Kings%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HC%20on%20Wednesday%20also%20waived%20the%20six-month%20cooling%20per