%20Moon's%20South%20Pole%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20then%20became%20only%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhistory-made-internet-erupts-in-pride-as-chandrayaan-3-successfully-lands-on-moon-4323035%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efourth%20country%20to%20successfully%20land%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20achieved%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20%2475%20million%20-%20a%20fraction%20of%20what%20NASA's%20missions%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20was%20able%20to%20land%20at%20the%20south%20pole%20(on%20the%20Moon)%20for%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20money%20the%20US%20spent...%20more%20power%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20praising%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%2C%20or%20ISRO%2C%20for%20the%20level%20of%20streamlining%20and%20efficiency%20in%20R%26amp%3BD%20and%20in%20building%20the%20rocket%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20costs%20of%20a%20space%20programme%2C%20Mr%20Tyson%20pointed%20out%20the%20money%20India%20allots%20to%20ISRO%2C%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20overall%20government%20funding%2C%20is%20almost%20the%20same%20amount%20as%20NASA%20gets%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discussion%20on%20India's%20space%20ambitions%20came%20out%20of%20a%20question%20about%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20the%20SpaceX%20rocket%20that%20brought%20Ms%20Williams%20and%20Mr%20Wilmore%20home.%20Mr%20Tyson%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20what%20role%20the%20private%20sector%20-%20in%20the%20US%20or%20India%20-%20could%20have%20in%20space%20exploration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20role%2C%20Mr%20Tyson%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20the%20private%20sector's%20involvement%20is%20necessary%20and%20natural%2C%20and%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20spoken%20to%20him%20about%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fneil-degrasse-tyson-ndtv-interview-sunita-williams-international-space-station-return-plastic-cups-for-now-neil-degrasse-tyson-on-sunita-williams-reco-7967107%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll_Imagetopscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNo%20Sympathy%20For%20Sunita%20Williams%20Because...%26quot%3B%3A%20Neil%20deGrasse%20Tyson%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20what%20SpaceX%20has%20done%20is%20more%20of%20what%20NASA%20has%20already%20done.%20NASA%20built%20the%20space%20station%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20space%20shuttle%2C%20literally.%20NASA%20took%20cargo%20and%20astronauts...%20and%20now%20SpaceX%2C%20and%20other%20possibly%20competing%20companies%2C%20can%20take%20cargo%20and%20astronauts%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20great.%20That%20is%20how%20it%20should%20be.%20The%20real%20value%20of%20private%20enterprises%20is%20that%20once%20they%20see%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done...%20they%20have%20the%20latitude%20to%20go%20out%20there%20and%20do%20it%20for%20less%20or%20more%20efficiently%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-chief-says-private-players-will-make-space-more-accessible-5544018%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BPrivate%20Players%20Will%20Make%20Space%20More%20Accessible%26quot%3B%3A%20ISRO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20more%20streamlining%20in%20private%20enterprise%20and%20this%20is%20expected%20because%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20the%20government%20is%20doing%20it%20first%2C%20then%20you%20don't%20even%20know%20how%20to%20streamline%20it%20because%20nobody%20has%20ever%20done%20this%20before%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20know%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20I%20spent%20some%20time%20with%20your%20Prime%20Minister.%20We%20chatted%20briefly%20during%20his%20trip%20to%20New%20York%20about%20future%20of%20space%20exploration%20in%20India%2C%20and%20he%20expressed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-lauds-pixxel-for-launching-india-first-private-satellite-constellation-7509697%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrong%20interest%20in%20bringing%20private%20enterprises%20into%20that%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20sees%20that%20this%20will%20be%20a%20natural%20evolution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20India's%20space%20dreams%2C%20Mr%20Tyson%20would%20not%20be%20drawn%20beyond%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20what%20matters%20are%20your%20ambitions%20and%20then%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20resources%2C%20you%20can%20achieve%20it%20slowly%20or%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%2C%20however%2C%20offer%20China%20as%20an%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20China%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20ISS%20(this%20was%20after%20the%20US%20objected%20to%20technology%20transfer)%2C%20they%20said%2C%20'okay%2C%20we%20will%20go%20into%20space%20on%20our%20own'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20had%20a%20growing%20economy%20and%20money%2C%20so%20they%20said%2C%20'we%20want%20to%20send%20our%20first%20astronauts'.%20And%20they%20did%20that.%20They%20said%2C%20'we%20want%20to%20put%20a%20rover%20on%20the%20Moon'.%20And%20they%20did%20that.%20They%20said%2C%20'we%20want%20to%20build%20our%20space%20station'.%20And%20they%20are%20doing%20that...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742464920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Frnq102go_neil-degrasse-tyson-and-pm-modi_625x300_21_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fneil-degrasse-tyson-ndtv-intervi