rget%20naval%20mines%2C%20which%20represent%20one%20of%20the%20most%20complex%20security%20problems%20facing%20shipping%20and%20maritime%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrench%20defense%20company%20Thales%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thalesgroup.com%2Fen%2Fworldwide%2Fdefence-and-security%2Fpress_release%2Fworld-first-thales-delivers-first-autonomous-drone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20delivery%20of%20the%20first%20of%20four%20Maritime%20Mine%20Counter%20Measures%20systems%20to%20France%20in%20February%2C%20and%20another%20to%20the%20UK%20%E2%80%94%20also%20the%20first%20of%20four%20%E2%80%94%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThales%20said%20MMCM's%20modular%20system%20allows%20for%20the%20detection%20and%20neutralization%20of%20naval%20mines%20without%20the%20need%20to%20send%20sailors%20into%20danger%20on%20crewed%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20countries%20paid%20a%20combined%20%24468%20million%20for%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288266b40-8b9c-428b-b017-c358320db3a7%5C%22%3EAn%20expensive%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELaying%20naval%20mines%20is%20a%20relatively%20inexpensive%20act%20that%20can%20have%20hugely%20expensive%20consequences%20on%20world%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMines%20laid%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20have%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblack-sea-naval-mine-clearance-ukraine-war-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20worrying%20problem%20for%20shipping%20lanes%20in%20the%20Black%20Sea%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20landmines%20tend%20to%20stay%20in%20one%20place%2C%20naval%20mines%20can%20sit%20at%20any%20depth%20and%20can%20become%20unmoored%20and%20begin%20to%20drift%2C%20making%20them%20particularly%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20so%20intractable%20that%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bdemining%26quot%3B%20doesn't%20even%20apply%20%E2%80%94%20the%20term%20at%20sea%20is%20%26quot%3Bmine%20countermeasures.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plume%20of%20water%20and%20some%20debris%20shoot%20out%20of%20the%20Black%20Sea%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Burgas%2C%20Bulgaria%2C%20on%20July%2022%202022%20during%20military%20mine%20countermeasures%20exercise%20Sea%20Breeze.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ec1e58cfb7f307e57300f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22674%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20naval%20mine%20explodes%20during%20a%20military%20exercise%20in%202022%20near%20Burgas%2C%20Bulgaria.%3Cp%3EHristo%20Rusev%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Morrison%2C%20Mine%20Countermeasures%20Delivery%20Director%20for%20Thales%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20transportation%20of%20the%20food%20and%20the%20energy%20sources%20for%20our%20homes%20%E2%80%94%20is%20under%20threat%20more%20than%20any%20time%20since%20WWII.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemote%20vehicles%20and%20drones%20are%20already%20used%20in%20naval%20mine%20countermeasures%20operations%2C%20but%20generally%20in%20combination%20with%20conventional%20crewed%20ships.%20Thales%20says%20its%20AI-powered%2C%20autonomous%20system%20can%20streamline%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20map%20the%20area%20and%20locate%20mines%2C%20an%20advanced%20sonar%20is%20towed%20along%20the%20water%20by%20a%2039-ft%20surface%20drone%20that%20can%20be%20controlled%20via%20the%20system's%20portable%20operations%20center%2C%20either%20on%20land%20or%20at%20sea%20up%20to%2014%20miles%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20mine%20has%20been%20detected%2C%20a%20remotely%20operated%20vehicle%2C%20or%20ROV%2C%20can%20be%20sent%20to%20neutralize%20it%2C%20under%20the%20control%20of%20personnel%20at%20the%20operations%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20vessels%20are%20fitted%20with%20AI%20automatic%20target%20detection%20and%20recognition%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20significantly%20speeds%20up%20the%20process%2C%20Morrison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20quantity%20of%20data%20operators%20have%20to%20process%20would%20swamp%20a%20human%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20Turkish%20Nav's%20minesweeper%20ship%20belonging%20to%20Turkish%20Navy%20Mine%20Squadron%20Command%20in%202022.%20An%20auxiliary%20boat%20and%20its%20circular%20trail%20in%20the%20water%20around%20the%20ship%20is%20also%20visible.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eafbc3cfb7f307e572aace%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThales%20says%20the%20system%20removes%20the%20need%20for%20crewed%20ships%2C%20such%20as%20this%20Turkish%20Navy%20minesweeper%2C%20to%20enter%20dangerous%20waters.%3Cp%3EAli%20Atmaca%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK's%20Royal%20Navy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royalnavy.mod.uk%2Fnews%2F2024%2Fdecember%2F12%2F20241212-apollo-trials-on-the-clyde-as-mine-hunting-tech-takes-step-forward%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20successful%20trial%20of%20the%20system's%20drone%20prototype%20in%20Scotland's%20Firth%20of%20Clyde%20late%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Sidharth%20Kaushal%2C%20a%20research%20fellow%20in%20sea%20power%20at%20the%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%2C%20the%20new%20tech%20is%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20significant%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20it's%20among%20one%20of%20the%20first%20truly%20autonomous%20systems%20to%20be%20fully%20operational.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20offers%20several%20advantages%2C%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20the%20efficiency%20gains%20of%20AI.%20%26quot%3BBut%20a%20more%20important%20factor%20is%20it%20provides%20stand-off%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaval%20mines%20are%20often%20clustered%20in%20or%20near%20active%20conflict%20zones%2C%20such%20as%20the%20port%20of%20Odesa%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmissiles-us-destroyer-same-ship-targeted-years-ago-in-area-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20narrow%20strip%20of%20water%20through%20which%20a%20third%20of%20the%20world's%20oil%20flows%20and%20which%20has%20long%20been%20threatened%20by%20Houthi%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20places%20like%20this%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20threat%20posed%20by%20naval%20mines%20overlaps%20with%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20things%20like%20anti-ship%20cruise%20missiles%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaushal%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20is%20%26quot%3Bobviously%20a%20pretty%20significant%20challenge%20for%20traditional%20mine%20countermeasures%20vessels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20despite%20its%20price%20tag%2C%20the%20new%20system%20is%20likely%20cheaper%20than%20traditional%20mine%20countermeasures%20vessels%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20there's%20also%20the%20additional%20advantage%20of%20not%20having%20to%20worry%20as%20much%20about%20losing%20crews.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrance-uk-thales-ai-naval-mine-hunting-drone-system-shipping-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742464581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d826f0b8b41a9673fad240%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrance-uk-thales-ai-naval-mine-hunting-drone-system-shipping-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Naval%20mines%20are%20an%20expensive%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20in%20lives%20and%20global%20trade.%20An%20AI-powered%20drone%20system%20bought%20by%20the%20UK%20and%20France%20could%20change%20that.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mjankowicz%40businessinsider.com%20(Mia%20Jankowicz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A61%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinside