liability%2C%20dispatchability%2C%20and%20flexibility%20provides%20India%20with%20a%20very%20appropriate%20element%20in%20the%20equation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Grossi%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expansion%20plan%20is%20ambitious%2C%20given%20that%20nuclear%20energy%20currently%20contributes%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20India's%20total%20electricity%20generation.%20However%2C%20Mr%20Grossi%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20India's%20capabilities.%20%26quot%3BIf%20any%20country%20can%20do%20it%2C%20it%20is%20India.%20India%20has%20the%20technological%20base%2C%20the%20industrial%20base%2C%20and%20the%20manpower.%20I%20don't%20see%20any%20major%20obstacles%20preventing%20this%20incremental%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Mr%20Grossi%20meeting%20Indias%20nuclear%20energy%20officials%20at%20the%20Kakrapar%20Nuclear%20Reactor%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Mr%20Grossi%20meeting%20Indias%20nuclear%20energy%20officials%20at%20the%20Kakrapar%20Nuclear%20Reactor%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F30hppj8_rafael-grossi-ndtv-_625x300_20_March_25.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Grossi%20meeting%20India's%20nuclear%20energy%20officials%20at%20the%20Kakrapar%20Nuclear%20Reactor%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20factors%20in%20this%20growth%20is%20Small%20Modular%20Reactors%20(SMRs)%2C%20which%20have%20garnered%20global%20attention.%20India's%20decision%20to%20explore%20SMRs%2C%20including%20the%20indigenous%20Bharat%20Small%20Reactor%20(BSR)%20initiative%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20effort%20to%20decarbonise%20energy-intensive%20industries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSMRs%20are%20popular%20because%20they%20offer%20several%20attractive%20characteristics.%20First%2C%20as%20their%20name%20suggests%2C%20they%20are%20smaller.%20This%20means%20they%20can%20be%20deployed%20faster%20and%20more%20easily.%20They%20may%20also%20be%20more%20accessible%20-%20not%20just%20for%20major%20global%20powers%20like%20India%2C%20but%20also%20for%20medium-sized%20and%20developing%20countries.%20I'm%20very%20pleased%20to%20see%20that%20India%20is%20exploring%20this%20as%20well%2C'%20Mr%20Grossi%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Need%20For%20Independent%20Nuclear%20Regulator%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20India's%20strong%20nuclear%20track%20record%2C%20one%20critical%20issue%20remains%20unresolved%3A%20regulatory%20independence.%20Mr%20Grossi%20batted%20for%20India's%20nuclear%20regulator%20to%20be%20independent%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20(DAE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20clearly%20the%20best%20practice.%20I%20see%20it%20worldwide.%20An%20independent%20regulator%20is%20extremely%20important%20because%20you%20need%20a%20technical%20body%20that%20speaks%20truth%20to%20power.%20It%20must%20be%20able%20to%20indicate%20when%20adjustments%20are%20needed.%20This%20is%20how%20we%20cultivate%20a%20strong%20safety%20and%20security%20culture.%20With%20an%20independent%20regulator%2C%20you%20can%20be%20sure%20that%20the%20system%20remains%20objective%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Grossi%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20nuclear%20regulation%20is%20overseen%20by%20the%20Atomic%20Energy%20Regulatory%20Board%20(AERB)%2C%20which%20reports%20to%20the%20DAE.%20Critics%20argue%20that%20this%20structure%20creates%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%2C%20as%20the%20same%20entity%20responsible%20for%20promoting%20nuclear%20power%20also%20regulates%20its%20safety.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Crumbling%20Of%20'Atoms%20for%20Peace'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20beyond%20India%2C%20Mr%20Grossi%20provided%20a%20sobering%20assessment%20of%20the%20state%20of%20global%20nuclear%20governance.%20The%20original%20vision%20of%20the%20IAEA%20-%20often%20summarised%20as%20'Atoms%20for%20Peace'%20-%20was%20to%20prevent%20nuclear%20weapons%20proliferation%20while%20promoting%20peaceful%20nuclear%20energy.%20However%2C%20Mr%20Grossi%20acknowledged%20the%20growing%20concerns%20that%20the%20agency%20has%20struggled%20to%20fully%20achieve%20either%20objective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20number%20of%20nuclear-armed%20nations%20has%20grown.%20However%2C%20I%20would%20argue%20that%20this%20growth%20has%20been%20relatively%20contained.%20Without%20the%20Non-Proliferation%20of%20Nuclear%20Weapons%20(NPT)%2C%20the%20IAEA%2C%20and%20the%20safeguard%20system%2C%20we%20would%20likely%20see%20dozens%20more%20nuclear-armed%20states%2C%20leading%20to%20greater%20international%20instability%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Grossi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Rafael%20Grossi%20with%20Indias%20nuclear%20chief%20Dr%20AK%20Mohanty.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Rafael%20Grossi%20with%20Indias%20nuclear%20chief%20Dr%20AK%20Mohanty.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F5dtj4v8g_rafael-grossi-ndtv-_625x300_20_March_25.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERafael%20Grossi%20with%20India's%20nuclear%20chief%20Dr%20AK%20Mohanty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20the%20IAEA%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20facilitating%20the%20safe%20introduction%20of%20nuclear%20energy.%20Through%20our%20safety%20standards%20and%20security%20initiatives%2C%20we%20ensure%20that%20nuclear%20technology%20is%20used%20responsibly%20-%20not%20just%20for%20power%20generation%20but%20also%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20cancer%20treatment%2C%20food%20security%2C%20and%20environmental%20protection.%20While%20I%20acknowledge%20the%20challenges%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20as%20harsh%20in%20my%20assessment.%20Every%20day%2C%20we%20work%20toward%20progress.%20That%20is%20why%20I%20am%20here%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20shifting%20geopolitical%20dynamics%2C%20particularly%20the%20United%20States'%20increasingly%20thorny%20equation%20with%20NATO%20under%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20fears%20of%20nuclear%20proliferation%20in%20Europe%20have%20intensified.%C2%A0These%20developments%20raise%20concerns%20about%20a%20new%20arms%20race.%20While%20the%20IAEA%20continues%20to%20advocate%20for%20non-proliferation%2C%20the%20challenge%20remains%20whether%20it%20can%20enforce%20nuclear%20restraint%20in%20an%20increasingly%20fragmented%20global%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Nuclear%20Capabilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20nuclear%20programme%20is%20unique%20in%20its%20end-to-end%20capabilities.%20Unlike%20many%20other%20nations%2C%20India%20mines%20its%20own%20uranium%2C%20designs%20and%20builds%20its%20own%20reactors%2C%20reprocesses%20spent%20nuclear%20fuel%20and%20has%20an%20extensive%20research%20and%20development%20infrastructure.%20This%20self-sufficiency%20has%20allowed%20India%20to%20maintain%20energy%20security%20while%20avoiding%20reliance%20on%20external%20suppliers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fgucosl7o_agni-missile_625x300_22_October_22.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgni%20Missile%20is%20capable%20of%20carrying%20nuclear%20warheads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Grossi%20acknowledged%20this%20strength%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BDuring%20my%20tenure%2C%20I%20worked%20closely%20with%20India%20and%20other%20aspiring%20nations%20because%20they%20had%20demonstrated%20their%20role%20as%20responsible%20global%20nuclear%20players%2C%20even%20outside%20the%20NPT%20framework.%20My%20view%20is%20that%20major%20nuclear%20stakeholders%20-%20like%20India%20-%20should%20be%20part%20of%20these%20discussions.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20sought%20full%20membership%20in%20the%20Nuclear%20Suppliers%20Group%20(NSG)%2C%20a%20consortium%20that%20controls%20nuclear%20trade.%20Mr%20Grossi%2C%20who%20previously%20presided%20over%20the%20NSG%2C%20expressed%20support%20for%20India's%20inclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Liability%20Debate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20major%20hurdle%20for%20international%20nuclear%20collaboration%20in%20India%20has%20been%20its%20Civil%20Nuclear%20Liability%20Act.%20The%20global%20nuclear%20liability%20regime%20is%20seen%20as%20industry-friendly%2C%20while%20India's%20Liability%20Act%20is%20viewed%20as%20people-friendly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20issue%20is%20complex%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20see%20it%20as%20a%20simple%20industry-versus-people%20debate.%20A%20strong%20liability%20framework%20is%20essential%2C%20providing%20adequate%20compensation%20in%20the%20unlikely%20event%20of%20an%20accident.%20Both%20sides%20should%20engage%20in%20dialogue%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Grossi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20a%20contentious%20issue%20in%20past%20negotiations%20with%20US%20and%20French%20nuclear%20suppliers%2C%20slowing%20down%20international%20nuclear%20projects%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThorium%3A%20India's%20Long-Term%20Bet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20long%20championed%20thorium-based%20nuclear%20energy%2C%20given%20its%20abundant%20thorium%20reserves.%20Unlike%20uranium%2C%20thorium-based%20reactors%20generate%20less%20long-lived%20radioactive%20waste%20and%20reduce%20proliferation%20risks.%20Mr%20Grossi%20acknowledged%20India's%20leadership%20in%20this%20area%20but%20noted%20that%20global%20nuclear%20infrastructure%20remains%20centred%20around%20uranium.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20global%20nuclear%20fuel%20cycle%20has%20traditionally%20relied%20on%20uranium%2C%20I%20believe%20thorium%20could%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20future.%20We%20do%20not%20advocate%20nuclear%20dominance%20but%20rather%20an%20intelligent%20energy%20mix%2C'%20Mr%20Grossi%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742464320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fguvcaug_grossi-exclusive-ndtv-_625x300_20_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbombs-atoms-gandhi-ndtv-exclusive-with-head-of-global-nuclear-watchdog-rafael-mariano-grossi-7967652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20portrait%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20International%20Atomic%20Energy%20Agency%20(IAEA)%2C%20Rafael%20Mariano%20Grossi%2C%20praised%20India's%20nuclear%20programme%20as%20safe%20and%20well-managed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbombs-atoms-gandhi-ndtv-exclusive-with-head-of-global-nuclear-watchdog-rafael-mariano-grossi-7967652%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20X%20sues%20Centre%20for%20using%20IT%20Act%20to%20'block'%20content%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742464180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119252205%2Cimgsize-13798.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Felon-musks-x-sues-centre-for-using-it-act-to-block-content%2Farticleshow%2F119250608.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20X%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20Indian%20government%20for%20allegedly%20misusing%20the%20IT%20Act%20to%20block%20content%20on%20the%20platform.%20The%20case%20challenges%20the%20interpretation%20of%20Section%2079(3)(b)%2C%20claiming%20it%20leads%20to%20arbitrary%20censorship%20and%20violates%20Supreme%20Court%20rulings.%20X%20seeks%20clearer%20guidelines%20and%20a%20proper%20judicial%20process%20for%20content%20blocking.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20Dark%20Energy%3F%20The%20Mystery%20Behind%20The%20Expanding%20Universe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDark%20energy%20makes%20up%20roughly%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20universe%2C%20yet%20we%20know%20nothing%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2025%20percent%20of%20the%20universe%20is%20the%20equally%20mysterious%20dark%20matter%2C%20leaving%20just%20five%20percent%20for%20everything%20that%20we%20can%20see%20and%20touch%20--%20matter%20made%20up%20of%20atoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDark%20energy%20is%20the%20placeholder%20name%20scientists%20have%20given%20to%20the%20unknown%20force%20causing%20the%20universe%20to%20expand%20faster%20and%20faster%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20recent%20cosmic%20clues%20have%20been%20chipping%20away%20at%20the%20leading%20theory%20for%20this%20phenomenon%2C%20which%20could%20eventually%20mean%20humanity%20will%20have%20to%20rethink%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20several%20new%20telescopes%20taking%20aim%20at%20the%20problem%2C%20scientists%20hope%20to%20have%20some%20concrete%20answers%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20what%20many%20scientists%20have%20called%20the%20greatest%20mystery%20in%20the%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20what%20is%20dark%20energy%20exactly%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20knows.%20It%20is%20invisible%20and%20it%20does%20not%20interact%20with%20matter%20or%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20may%20not%20even%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20begins%20--%20like%20everything%20else%20--%20at%20the%20Big%20Bang%20around%2013.8%20billion%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20the%20universe%20first%20started%20expanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bcosmic%20tug-of-war%26quot%3B%20between%20two%20mysterious%20forces%2C%20Joshua%20Frieman%2C%20a%20theoretical%20astrophysicist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDark%20matter%20is%20thought%20to%20pull%20galaxies%20together%2C%20while%20dark%20energy%20pushes%20them%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20first%20nine%20or%20so%20billion%20years%20of%20the%20universe%2C%20%26quot%3Bdark%20matter%20was%20winning%2C%26quot%3B%20forming%20galaxies%20and%20everything%20else%2C%20Frieman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20dark%20energy%20gained%20the%20upper%20hand%2C%20starting%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20for%20most%20of%20history%2C%20scientists%20had%20little%20idea%20this%20almighty%20tussle%20was%20going%20on.%20They%20thought%20that%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20universe%20would%20simply%20start%20to%20slow%20down%20because%20of%20gravity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverything%20changed%20in%201998%20when%20two%20separate%20groups%20of%20astronomers%20noticed%20that%20distant%20exploding%20stars%20called%20supernovae%20were%20farther%20away%20than%20they%20ought%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20to%20the%20discovery%20that%20the%20universe%20is%20not%20just%20expanding%20--%20it%20is%20do%20so%20faster%20and%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20could%20be%20causing%20this%20acceleration%3F%20They%20gave%20this%20strange%20force%20a%20name%3A%20dark%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20main%20theories%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leading%20theory%20has%20long%20been%20that%20empty%20space%20itself%20produces%20dark%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%2C%20Frieman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20remove%20all%20the%20particles%20from%20the%20cup%20of%20coffee%2C%20there%20is%20still%20energy%20in%20there%20due%20to%20what%20we%20call%20the%20quantum%20vacuum%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20energy%20of%20empty%20space%20is%20known%20as%20the%20cosmological%20constant.%20It%20is%20the%20theory%20used%20in%20the%20standard%20model%20of%20cosmology%2C%20Lambda-CDM%2C%20which%20is%20our%20best%20guess%20for%20how%20the%20universe%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20several%20scientific%20results%20have%20appeared%20to%20support%20a%20rival%20theory%20--%20called%20evolving%20dark%20energy%20--%20which%20has%20brought%20the%20standard%20model%20into%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20new%20results%20from%20the%20Dark%20Energy%20Spectroscopic%20Instrument%20provided%20the%20latest%20signs%20that%20dark%20energy%20could%20actually%20be%20weakening%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20scientists%20behind%20the%20research%20emphasise%20there%20is%20not%20yet%20definitive%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20proven%20right%2C%20this%20would%20rule%20out%20that%20dark%20energy%20is%20a%20cosmological%20constant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20not%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20energy%20of%20empty%20space%20--%20because%20empty%20space%20doesn't%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Frieman%2C%20a%20leading%20proponent%20of%20the%20theory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20dark%20matter%20to%20change%2C%20it%20would%20likely%20require%20the%20existence%20of%20some%20incredibly%20light%2C%20as-yet-unknown%20particle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20possibility%20is%20that%20there%20is%20something%20wrong%20with%20our%20calculations%20--%20or%20our%20understanding%20of%20gravity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEinstein's%20theory%20of%20relativity%20has%20withstood%20an%20incredible%20amount%20of%20scientific%20scrutiny%20over%20the%20last%20century%2C%20and%20has%20been%20proven%20right%20again%20and%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20Einstein%20was%20wrong%2C%20but%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20bit%20of%20room%26quot%3B%20to%20change%20his%20theory%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20largest%20scales%20of%20the%20universe%2C%20Frieman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20could%20we%20know%20more%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon.%20The%20best%20way%20to%20understand%20dark%20energy%20is%20to%20look%20at%20a%20vast%20swathe%20of%20sky%2C%20taking%20in%20as%20many%20galaxies%20with%20as%20much%20data%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20a%20bunch%20of%20new%20telescopes%20are%20working%20to%20do%20just%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Europe's%20Euclid%20space%20telescope%20released%20its%20first%20astronomical%20data%20since%20launching%20in%202023%20--%20but%20any%20dark%20energy%20results%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA's%20Nancy%20Grace%20Roman%20space%20telescope%2C%20planned%20for%20launch%20in%202027%2C%20and%20the%20under-construction%20Vera%20Rubin%20Observatory%20in%20Chile%20will%20also%20take%20aim%20at%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20an%20exciting%20time%20for%20dark%20energy%2C%20Frieman%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20expected%20a%20%26quot%3Bdefinitive%20answer%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20time%20to%20waste%2C%20Frieman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20minute%20we%20wait%2C%20galaxies%20are%20disappearing%20from%20view.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742463960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F5ualdjfg_dark-energy-_625x300_20_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdark-energy-explained-the-mystery-behind-the-expanding-universe-7966009%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dark%20energy%20makes%20up%20roughly%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20universe%2C%20yet%20we%20know%20nothing%20about%20it.%20Around%2025%20percent%20of%20the%20universe%20is%20the%20equally%20mysterious%20dark%20matter%2C%20leaving%20just%20five%20percent%20for%20everything%20that%2