year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoint%20Sword-2024%20A%20occurred%20in%20May%2C%20while%20Joint%20Sword-2024%20B%20took%20place%20in%20October.%20Both%20involved%20elements%20of%20the%20PLA%20conducting%20demonstrations%20around%20Taiwan.%20May's%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-taiwans-election-results-mean-for-relations-with-china-us-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaiwanese%20President%20Lai%20Ching-te%3C%2Fa%3E's%20inauguration%20and%20October's%20after%20Taiwanese%20Independence%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drills%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20Taiwan%20and%20its%20international%20partners%2C%20but%20there%20was%20more%20to%20it%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20developments%20seen%20in%202025%20so%20far%20indicate%20the%20PLA%20Navy%20specifically%20is%20enhancing%20its%20realistic%20combat%20training%2C%20per%20Tang.%20The%20first%20is%20that%20PLA%20Navy%20activities%20around%20Taiwan%20have%20seen%20an%20overall%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENumbers%20from%20Taiwan's%20Ministry%20of%20Defense%20indicate%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20PLAN%20vessels%20operating%20near%20Taiwan%20compared%20to%20previous%20years%2C%20419%20in%20the%20first%20two%20months%20of%20this%20year%20compared%20to%20305%20in%202024%20and%20218%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20number%20of%20joint%20combat%20readiness%20patrols%20involving%20assets%20from%20multiple%20military%20branches%2C%20such%20as%20PLAN%20vessels%20and%20PLA%20Air%20Force%20planes%2C%20are%20higher%20as%20well.%20And%20the%20number%20of%20PLAN%20ships%20involved%20in%20these%20patrols%20is%20up%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Chinese%20vessel%20sailing%20the%20open%20ocean.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6658911acc442a2f676c2912%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221348%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screen%20grab%20captured%20from%2