nsider.com%2Fai-search-company-glean-launches-digital-agents-for-businesses-2025-2%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlean%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20released%20agents%20or%20agent-related%20products%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-agents-internet-dark-google-openai-anthropic-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAgents%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20are%20one%20of%20the%20buzziest%20topics%20in%20AI%2C%20and%20companies%20have%20been%20rolling%20out%20one%20after%20another%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20few%20agree%20on%20what%20they%20actually%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-launches-operator-ai-agent-book-reservations-buy-products-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20released%20Operator%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20agent%20that%20can%20browse%20the%20web%2C%20book%20travel%20tickets%2C%20and%20create%20memes.%20Enterprise%20technology%20companies%20from%20Glean%20to%20Cohere%20have%20unveiled%20platforms%20that%20allow%20employees%20to%20build%20and%20deploy%20agents.%20And%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Chinese%20startup%20Butterfly%20Effect%20drummed%20up%20DeepSeek-level%20buzz%20by%20unveiling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanus-ai-china-agent-hype-deepseek-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20invite-only%20AI%20agent%20that%20can%20analyze%20stocks%2C%20scrape%20data%20off%20the%20web%2C%20and%20even%20create%20interactive%20websites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgents%20are%20commonly%20defined%20as%20virtual%20assistants%20that%20can%20complete%20tasks%20autonomously.%20They%20break%20down%20problems%2C%20outline%20plans%2C%20and%20take%20action%20without%20being%20prompted%20by%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20excitement%20around%20them%20is%20that%20they%20might%20be%20the%20first%20step%20to%20a%20hands-free%20world%20where%20humans%20can%20sit%20back%2C%20relax%2C%20and%20watch%20AI%20do%20all%20the%20work.%20But%20AI%20experts%20who%20work%20with%20agentic%20systems%20say%20the%20tech%20is%20more%20nuanced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%E2%80%8AI've%20heard%20definitions%20of%20agents%20where%20something%20is%20only%20an%20agent%20if%20it%20takes%20actions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Douwe%20Kiela%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Contextual%20AI%2C%20which%20helps%20companies%20build%20and%20deploy%20RAG%20agents.%20Kiela%20previously%20led%20the%20team%20at%20Meta%20that%20developed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretrieval-augmented-generation-making-ai-language-models-better-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretrieval%20augmented%20generation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20RAG%2C%20a%20technique%20that%20enhances%20the%20outputs%20of%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%E2%80%8AThink%20of%20Deep%20Research%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20in%20reference%20to%20agents%20developed%20by%20OpenAI%2C%20Perplexity%2C%20and%20Google%20that%20synthesize%20hundreds%20of%20online%20sources%20into%20detailed%20reports.%20%26quot%3BThat%20doesn't%20necessarily%20take%20any%20actions%20besides%20search.%20Is%20that%20an%20agent%3F%20I%20would%20say%20yes%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20say%20no%2C%20it%20has%20to%20take%20actions%20that%20somehow%20affect%20the%20state%20or%20the%20environment%20the%20agent%20operates%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20correct%20definition%20of%20an%20agent%20is%20simply%20something%20that%20%26quot%3Bactively%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20Kiela%20said.%20%26quot%3B%E2%80%8ASo%20if%20it%20made%20a%20mistake%2C%20then%20they%20can%20catch%20that%20mistake%20and%20try%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENatural%20language%20expert%20Satya%20Nitta%2C%20CEO%20of%20Emergence%20AI%2C%20a%20company%20specializing%20in%20multi-agent%20syste