ned%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wthr.com%2Farticle%2Fnews%2Fcrime%2Fbrittany-fortinberry-five-new-victims-child-molestation-sex-abuse-martinsville-morgan-county-eminence-misconduct-teacher-snapchat-session-nudes%2F531-50db55a1-f0f1-49fa-bb0f-55fa1c8f8efa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETV%20station%20WTHR%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Fortinberry%20allegedly%20provided%20drugs%20to%20the%20teens%20and%20forced%20them%20to%20have%20sex.%20In%20one%20instance%2C%20she%20reportedly%20drugged%20a%20victim%20multiple%20times%20before%20assaulting%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20teacher%20is%20also%20accused%20of%20threatening%20to%20take%20her%20own%20life%20if%20any%20of%20the%20victims%20reported%20the%20abuse.%20While%20many%20guardians%20remained%20unaware%20of%20the%20abuse%20until%20a%20Department%20of%20Child%20Services%20investigation%2C%20one%20parent%20claimed%20that%20Fortinberry's%20husband%20was%20complicit.%20According%20to%20court%20documents%2C%20the%20husband%20allegedly%20threatened%20to%20%26quot%3Bslaughter%26quot%3B%20a%20teen%20in%20front%20of%20Fortinberry%20if%20he%20reported%20the%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20documents%20show%20that%20Fortinberry%20used%20Snapchat%20and%20the%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Session%20to%20send%20nude%20and%20explicit%20images%20to%20her%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20victim%20recounted%20that%20she%20would%20wait%20for%20her%20children%20to%20fall%20asleep%20before%20initiating%20sexual%20contact%20with%20the%20boys.%20Another%20claimed%20she%20assaulted%20him%20after%20asking%20him%20to%20babysit%20her%20kids.%20Another%20teen%20alleged%20that%20when%20the%20boys%20resisted%20her%20advances%2C%20she%20would%20rape%20them%2C%20telling%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bjust%20let%20it%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20earlier%20case%2C%20Fortinberry%20was%20accused%20of%20abusing%20several%20students%20but%20attempted%20to%20blame%20h