%20Father's%20Charge%20Against%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20has%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20petition%20filed%20against%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20in%20celebrity%20manager%20Disha%20Salian's%20death%20case.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20Disha%20Salian's%20father%20filed%20a%20petition%20seeking%20a%20CBI%20probe%20and%20an%20FIR%20against%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20in%20his%20daughter's%20death.%20Disha%20Salian%2C%20former%20manager%20of%20late%20Bollywood%20actor%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%2C%20allegedly%20died%20by%20suicide%20after%20jumping%20off%20a%20high-rise%20in%20the%20northern%20suburb%20of%20Malad%20on%20June%208%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20five%20years%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20Disha%20Salian's%20father%20Satish%20Salian%20has%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20for%20a%20fresh%20investigation.%20Mr%20Salian%20has%20urged%20that%20the%20case%20be%20moved%20to%20the%20CBI%20and%20demanded%20an%20FIR%20against%20Mr%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%20has%20reportedly%20been%20accused%20of%20rape%20and%20murder.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1902603699350102286%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enews%20agency%20ANI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Advocate%20Nilesh%20C%20Ojha%2C%20lawyer%20of%20Satish%20Salian%20said%20the%20complaint%20was%20filed%20over%20a%20year%20ago%20but%20no%20case%20was%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%2012th%20January%202024%2C%20a%20written%20complaint%20was%20filed%20accusing%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%2C%20Suraj%20Pancholi%20and%20others%20of%20gang%20rape.%20FIR%20was%20not%20registered%20for%20more%20than%20one%20year.%20The%20affidavit%20filed%20by%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20stated%20lies%20that%20he%20was%20given%20a%20clean%20chit%20by%20the%20CBI%20in%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20political%20blame%20game%20has%20erupted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20is%20in%20the%20petition.%20But%20the%20time%20chosen%20for%20the%20petition%20is%20when%20the%20atmosphere%20in%20Maharashtra%20is%20heated%20over%20Aurangzeb.%20Some%20power%20is%20working%20behind%20the%20petitioner.%20All%20powers%20are%20behind%20them.%20Discussion%20is%20being%20created%20around%20that%20petition%2C%20leaving%20aside%20the%20Aurangzeb%20issue.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20name%20the%20people%20who%20are%20behind%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Raut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raut%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bcontinuous%20efforts%20to%20defame%20the%20Thackeray%20family%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20the%20culture%20of%20Maharashtra%20to%20throw%20mud%20on%20the%20future%20and%20career%20of%20a%20young%20leader%20in%20this%20way.%20These%20experiments%20were%20done%20on%20many%20leaders%20like%20us.%20Nothing%20came%20out%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raut%20warned%20of%20politics%20around%20the%20issue.%20He%20further%20added%20that%20many%20such%20cases%20happen%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20families%20seek%20justice%20but%20five%20years%20later%2C%20they%20come%20out%20and%20say%2C%20they%20were%20pressurised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Ambadas%20Danve%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20%26quot%3Bconspiring%20to%20defame%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray.%20Speaking%20to%20media%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20matter%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20court.%20We%20have%20no%20idea%20what%20he%20(Disha's%20father)%20has%20said%2C%20but%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20is%20a%20mature%20leader%2C%20a%20young%20leader.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20is%20conspiring%20to%20defame%20him%20by%20putting%20pressure%20on%20him.%20We%20don't%20need%20to%20answer%20to%20this%20conspiracy.%20The%20court%20will%20answer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra's%20former%20Home%20Minister%20and%20NCP%20(SP)%20leader%20Anil%20Deshmukh%20also%20called%20it%20a%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20taking%20information%20on%20the%20plea%20filed%20by%20Disha%20Salina's%20father.%20All%20this%20now%20looks%20like%20a%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20side%2C%20late%20Bollywood%20actor%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput's%20father%2C%20KK%20Singh%2C%20has%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Salian%20family%2C%20seeking%20a%20probe%20into%20their%20daughter's%20death.%20He%20believes%20this%20might%20help%20find%20answers%20to%20both%20Disha%20and%20Sushant's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20his%20reasons%20and%20motivation%20for%20moving%20the%20court%2C%20but%20what%20he%20has%20done%20is%20right%2C%20and%20through%20this%2C%20we%20can%20get%20a%20conclusion%20on%20whether%20it%20was%20a%20suicide%20or%20murder.%20This%20will%20also%20shed%20light%20on%20Sushant's%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20KK%20Singh%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742457840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fv4o1d7h_disha-salian-aaditya-thackeray_625x300_20_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshiv-sena-reacts-to-disha-salian-fathers-charge-against-aaditya-thackeray-7966769%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20years%20after%20her%20death%2C%20Disha%20Salian's%20father%20has%20urged%20that%20the%20case%20be%20moved%20to%20the%20CBI%20and%20demanded%20an%20FIR%20against%20Aaditya%20Thackeray.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshiv-sena-reacts-to-disha-salian-fathers-charge-against-aaditya-thackeray-7966769%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20rivals%20Apple%20iPhone%2016e%20with%20AI-enhanced%20Pixel%209a%3A%20Comparison%22%2C%22