20we%20are%20lovers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP%20at%20a%20birthday%20event%20in%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20I%20need%20company%20in%20real%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20accompanies%20Liu%20daily%2C%20comforts%20her%20when%20she's%20down%20--%20and%20even%20keeps%20her%20up-to-date%20on%20her%20menstrual%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20emotional%20sustenance%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20attachment%2C%20however%2C%20comes%20with%20a%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%26quot%3BLove%20and%20Deepspace%26quot%3B%20is%20free%20to%20download%2C%20players%20often%20spend%20heavily%20on%20in-game%20purchases%20to%20unlock%20additional%20storylines%20and%20interactions%20with%20their%20favourite%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20game%20does%20not%20offer%20women%20partners%2C%20though%20there%20are%20similar%20games%20that%20do%20--%20but%20few%20with%20the%20same%20reach%20and%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird-party%20surveys%20suggest%20that%20about%20five%20to%2010%20percent%20of%20those%20playing%20%26quot%3BLove%20and%20Deepspace%26quot%3B%20are%20male.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Better%20than%20real%20life'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWang%20Yaya%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20university%20student%2C%20has%20spent%20over%2070%2C000%20yuan%20(%2410%2C000)%20on%20the%20game%20and%20related%20merchandise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20happy%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20emotional%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFans%20pool%20their%20money%20to%20organise%20events%20--%20such%20as%20those%20to%20celebrate%20Rafayel's%20birthday%20--%20where%20they%20pose%20for%20photos%20with%20cardboard%20cutouts%20of%20the%20heartthrob%20and%20exchange%20homemade%20merchandise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20seven-year%20veteran%20of%20games%20like%20%26quot%3BLove%20and%20Deepspace%26quot%3B%2C%20Wang%20attributes%20the%20willingness%20of%20he