est%20political%20battle%20of%20his%20life.%20He%20has%20to%20deftly%20handle%20relationships%20with%20a%20stronger%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20the%20state%2C%20win%20elections%20due%20in%20Bihar%20in%20six%20months%2C%20and%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20ensure%20a%20bright%20future%20for%20his%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Who%20after%20Nitish'%3F%20The%20chorus%20around%20this%20question%20is%20growing%20in%20Bihar%20and%20the%20JD(U)'s%20circles.%20Will%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20son%20Nishant%20formally%20join%20politics%20and%20be%20named%20as%20his%20successor%3F%20Will%20the%20JD(U)%20disintegrate%20after%20the%20Bihar%20elections%3F%20Will%20it%20formally%20merge%20with%20the%20BJP%3F%20Or%2C%20will%20JD(U)%20leaders%20join%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20and%20other%20parties%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20JD(U)%20was%20formed%20by%20the%20members%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Janata%20Dal%20in%20Bihar.%20Also%2C%20many%20of%20the%20RJD's%20leaders%20joined%20the%20JD(U)%20in%20the%20past%20as%20their%20party%20weakened.%20It's%20a%20common%20joke%20in%20Bihar%20that%20the%20membership%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20is%20complementary%2C%20with%20easy%20to%20and%20fro%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENitish%20Is%20JD(U)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20is%20a%20good%20example%20of%20personality%20cults%20in%20Indian%20politics%3A%20he%20is%20JD(U)%2C%20and%20JD(U)%20is%20him.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20has%20managed%20to%20crush%20all%20competition%20within%20the%20party.%20Years%20ago%2C%20he%20had%20propped%20Sharad%20Yadav%20against%20George%20Fernandes%2C%20and%20then%20dumped%20Yadav%20when%20he%20tried%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20parallel%20power%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish's%20earlier%20attempts%20to%20have%20a%20succession%20plan%20have%20failed.%20He%20fell%20out%20with%20political%20strategist%20Prashant%20Kishor%2C%20whom%20he%20had%20even%20made%20the%20party's%20Vice-President%20at%20one%20point%2C%20and%20RCP%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20once%20seen%20as%20Nitish's%20number-two%20in%20the%20party.%20It%20also%20doesn't%20help%20that%20his%20close%20confidantes%2C%20namely%2C%20Lallan%20Singh%2C%20Ashok%20Chaudhary%20and%20Sanjay%20Jha%2C%20lack%20charisma%20and%20statewide%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20regional%20parties%20in%20India%20are%20family-controlled.%20This%20acts%20as%20a%20glue%20and%20keeps%20various%20factions%20together.%20Parties%20that%20do%20not%20have%20a%20family%20at%20the%20helm%20or%20a%20clear%20succession%20plan%20are%20today%20facing%20existential%20crises%2C%20like%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20in%20Odisha%2C%20Jayalalitha's%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Awkward%20Question%20About%20Nishant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%2C%20now%20in%20the%20last%20leg%20of%20his%20career%2C%20is%20aware%20that%20the%20party%20needs%20a%20successor%20to%20survive%20after%20him.%20There%20is%20a%20strong%20buzz%20that%20his%20son%20Nishant%20is%20likely%20to%20formally%20join%20politics%20and%20even%20contest%20elections.%20But%20Nishant%20so%20far%20hasn't%20been%20much%20of%20a%20public%20figure.%20His%20first%20major%20appearance%20was%20on%20January%208%2C%20when%20he%20visited%20his%20native%20village%2C%20Kalyan%20Bigha%2C%20with%20his%20father%20to%20pay%20tribute%20to%20freedom%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20Nishant%20has%20been%20seen%20attending%20party%20meetings%20and%20social%20gatherings%2C%20including%20Holi%20celebrations%2C%20even%20giving%20bytes%20to%20the%20media.%20He%20has%20strongly%20suggested%20that%20the%20NDA%20should%20name%20his%20father%20as%20its%20chief%20ministerial%20face.%20But%20he%20has%20displayed%20a%20visible%20disinclination%20towards%20politics%20in%20the%20past.%20Nitish%20himself%20has%20long%20opposed%20dynastic%20politics%2C%20following%20the%20example%20of%20his%20mentor%2C%20Karpoori%20Thakur%2C%20who%20kept%20his%20family%20away%20from%20politics.%20His%20criticism%20of%20Lalu%20Yadav%20for%20promoting%20family%20members%20in%20politics%20is%20well-known.%20So%2C%20this%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20an%20easy%20decision%20for%20Nitish%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Nishant%20is%20announced%20as%20a%20successor%2C%20he%20could%20face%20opposition%20from%20senior%20leaders%20in%20the%20party.%20The%20JD(U)%20could%20implode%20and%20some%20leaders%20may%20rebel%2C%20turning%20towards%20BJP%2C%20RJD%2C%20or%20even%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20this%20seems%20like%20the%20most%20viable%20option%20for%20the%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20One%20Want%20A%20Rudderless%20Ship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Nishant%20is%20not%20named%20as%20a%20successor%2C%20a%20battle%20could%20break%20out%20amongst%20seniors%20like%20Lallan%20Singh%2C%20Ashok%20Chaudhary%20or%20Sanjay%20Jha%20for%20the%20party's%20control.%20And%20the%20BJP%2C%20sensing%20an%20opportunity%2C%20might%20push%20for%20a%20merger%20to%20strengthen%20its%20base%20in%20the%20state.%20Some%20MLAs%20could%20still%20defect%20to%20other%20parties%2C%20but%20the%20party%20might%20survive%20as%20an%20entity%20at%20least%20with%20Nishant%20at%20the%20helm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiming%20is%20crucial.%20A%20transition%20is%20easier%20when%20a%20party%20is%20in%20power%2C%20as%20was%20the%20case%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20(SP)%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20with%20Lalu's%20son%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20a%20party%20has%20the%20luxury%20of%20quelling%20discontent%20by%20offering%20cabinet%20positions%20to%20disgruntled%20leaders.%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20had%20made%20Akhilesh%20the%20chief%20minister%20after%20his%20party's%20grand%20victory%20in%20the%202012%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20elections.%20Similarly%2C%20Lalu%20Yadav%20announced%20Tejashwi%20as%20his%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20after%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20won%20the%202015%20elections%20in%20Bihar.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20transferred%20the%20baton%20to%20Rahul%20in%202017%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20out%20of%20power%3B%20the%20move%20had%20ended%20up%20irking%20a%20host%20of%20leaders%2C%20particularly%20the%20%E2%80%98G-23'%20and%20the%20old%20guard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20if%20Nishant%20has%20to%20enter%20politics%2C%20this%20is%20the%20right%20time.%20It%20would%20signal%20to%20senior%20leaders%20who%20the%20boss%20is.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20party%20is%20in%20power%20will%20also%20help%20Nitish%20crush%20a%20possible%20rebellion%20using%20a%20carrot-and-stick%20policy.%20Sure%2C%20Nishant%20may%20face%20challenges%20as%20he%20doesn't%20have%20political%20experience%2C%20but%20the%20move%20could%20prevent%20an%20existential%20implosion%20within%20the%20JD(U)%20after%20Nitish%20calls%20it%20a%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742456700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fp4fmi2ho_nitish-kumar-ani_625x300_28_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fimplosion-or-rebellion-a-post-nitish-jd-u-will-not-be-pretty-7966608%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20Nishant%20is%20announced%20as%20a%20successor%2C%20he%20could%20face%20opposition%20from%20senior%20leaders%20in%20the%20party.%20If%20he%20is%20not%2C%20though%2C%20the%20party%20might%20implode.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUr