format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20grandfather%20would%20be%20thrilled%20about%20his%20grandson%E2%80%99s%20noble%20mission.%20He%E2%80%99d%20probably%20chuckle%20at%20how%20his%20attitude%20towards%20the%20sparrows%20has%20taken%20a%20complete%20180-degree%20turn.%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20catch%20sparrows%20when%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rakesh%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20used%20to%20make%20their%20nests%20on%20top%20of%20the%20fans%20in%20our%20home.%20My%20grandfather%20would%20warn%20me%20that%20if%20I%20switched%20the%20fan%20on%2C%20I%20would%20get%20into%20trouble.%E2%80%9D%20Those%20days%20are%20long%20behind%20him.%20School%20was%20followed%20by%20college%2C%20which%20was%20followed%20by%20years%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F368091%2Fvibha-bakshi-documentary-filmmaker-son-rise-daughters-of-mother-india-challenging-patriarchy-haryana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edocumentary%20filmmaking%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20time%20he%20had%20just%20resigned%20from%20one%20of%20his%20roles%2C%20he%20shares%20how%20he%20was%20in%20a%20proverbial%20slump.%20The%20garden%20near%20his%20house%20was%20his%20favourite%20retreat.%20And%2C%20the%20sparrows%20and%20squirrels%20never%20failed%20to%20check%20in%20on%20him.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20I%20think%20of%20it%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20probably%20how%20I%20tided%20through%20that%20phase%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%202008%20that%20Rakesh%2C%20realising%20that%20the%20corner%20office%20would%20never%20rival%20the%20happiness%20he%20felt%20when%20he%20was%20around%20birds%2C%20decided%20to%20turn%20all%20his%20attention%20to%20nest-making.%20And%20the%20accolades%20that%20followed%20%E2%80%94%20the%20National%20Science%20Award%20(2020)%2C%20mention%20in%20the%20Limca%20Book%20of%20World%2